            <div class="title">
                15 Amendment Of Law
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1945-10-23/debates/dd48b2dc-4bdf-4bd7-8aec-caf105f471ef/AcquisitionOfLane(Owner-Occupier)Regulations" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
